  (16305,0,1366,'Start','The warm night and the sunny morning did not make it easier to get that well deserved sleep. \nToo many hours was lost to your open eyes and thoughts about why this all happened. \nYou stand up and, yes, what do you do?\n',NULL,'root','2019-06-26 10:14:21','0000-00-00 00:00:00',345,100),
